    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-04-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-04-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="114" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d114">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Egan</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-04-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 25,
                            1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Blaine informs Mr. Egan that he can act with the Brazilian minister and
                        the French chargé d’affaires as mediator.</p>
            </div>
